description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Erwinia carotovora var. chrysanthemi; Erwinia chrysanhemi; Erwinia chrysanthemi; Pectobacterium carotovorum var. chrysanthemi; Pectobacterium cartovorum f. sp. chrysanthemi; Pectobacterium chrysanthemi; Pectobacterium chrysanthemi = Erwinia chrysanthemi; Pectobacterium parthenii; Pectobacterium parthenii var. chrysanthemi; Pectobacterium parthenii var. dianthicola.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
